The paper discusses the challenges and techniques related to hardware-aware modeling and optimization for deep learning applications. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer architecture (cs.AR), control systems (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
